Particulars of distribution of spawning: Coho throughout system, chums in lower sections.
COMMENTS ON CONDITIONS AFFECTING THIS ST: (11) Bank erosion: Bank erosion after 17 Nov. flooding on the lower reaches. (14) Flood: High water and flooding much of fall. Massive flood impacted all area 14 streams at peak migration period. (13) Drought: Low flows during the summer months reduced coho habitat in main stem. Lakes in the upper reaches, and small lake lower support the fry survival.
